---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Understanding Final Mile Delivery: What Brands Need To Know - parcelLab"
  description="Final mile delivery represents the supply chain stage where goods travel from distribution hubs to customer destinations, directly impacting customer satisfaction."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Delivery Experience</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Understanding Final Mile Delivery: What Brands Need To Know</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2022-04-30">April 30, 2022</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>7 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          The final mile, also called the last mile, is the supply chain stage where goods travel to their final destination. Although this seems straightforward, last mile logistics are increasingly complex and costly, given the immense coordination needed for on-time delivery.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Why Final Mile Delivery Matters</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Improve customer experience</strong> with personalized, real-time updates</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Better manage customer expectations</strong> with proactive delay notifications</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Reduce returns and chargebacks</strong> through proactive notifications</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Minimize customer support calls</strong> with real-time progress updates</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">How to Successfully Implement Final Mile Delivery</h2>
        <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Centralize orders</strong> into one platform for a single source of truth</li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Use an Operations Experience Management platform</strong> to turn complex data into actionable solutions</li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Ensure real-time visibility</strong> with integrations for all major carriers</li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Prioritize customer communication</strong> through order status pages, SMS, and chatbots</li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Analyze last mile data</strong> to optimize routes and reduce costs</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The final mile experience is an opportunity brands can't miss. With customers expecting seamless, branded experiences even post-checkout, matching their expectations is essential.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
